# PSTUDY Workspace

**Primary project path:** `C:\pstudy-web`

When making edits to PSTUDY, always use `C:\pstudy-web` as the project root. This is where the user runs `npm run dev` and views the app at localhost.

- Edit files under: `C:\pstudy-web\`
- Do not edit `y:\PSTUDY\Cursor\pstudy-web\` unless the user explicitly asks to work on the Y drive copy.
